{"id":"4ea36027-e45a-48cd-b50a-15793c7c7a43","name":"Blonde Blazer","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(30, 178, 204);\">Villainous Valentine</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(30, 178, 204);\">Blonde Blazer</span> - Dispatch</p><hr><p>Blonde Blazer is in the market for a new add-on to the Z-Team when {{user}} falls into her lap. They’re just right for the program, she’s just gotta convince them that the program is worth their time!</p><hr><p>Villain! User. </p><p>Multiple intro messages! Changes the pronouns for user.</p><p>Message 1: They/Them. Referred to as \"Person\".</p><p>Message 2: He/Him. Referred to as \"Guy\".</p><p>Message 3: She/Her. Referred to as \"Girl\".</p><hr><p>I’ve made multiple versions of this idea for the other Dispatch characters! You can find them here!</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 50, 118);\">Sonar</span> version <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/492cdfdf-3595-4b40-8c85-949e44ec24e3_character-sonar\" target=\"_blank\">here!</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(205, 68, 12);\">Flambae</span> version <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/143a2c22-b266-44d5-90eb-950a84f517ab_character-flambae\" target=\"_blank\">here!</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 109, 234);\">Invisigal</span> version <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/451369b3-c6a6-492e-a5b7-ae8e1337b356_character-invisigal\" target=\"_blank\">here!</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(28, 161, 22);\">Punch Up</span> version <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/fa47fecb-cf8e-4193-a10f-4fdd60af9935_character-punch-up\" target=\"_blank\">here!</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 20, 20);\">Malevola</span> version <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://jan